{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act19side", "eventName": "綠野幻夢", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "DV-S-2", "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "衡慮", "storyInfo": "年輕人總是會為一時的意氣相投而聚在一起，又在之後的漫長歲月裡認清彼此。無論最終如何，在相遇時，他們多少還是真心的。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "29_g2_edgeofbase", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$drift_intro", "key": "$drift_loop", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$transmission", "volume": 0.9}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_528_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "萊茵防衛科成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_528_1#1$1"}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......是我。", "name": "萊茵防衛科成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_528_1#1$1"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您猜得沒錯，警長選擇了幫那群拓荒者。還有埃琳娜·烏比卡，她也背叛了克魯尼主任。", "name": "萊茵防衛科成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_528_1#1$1"}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "通訊器另一頭傳來一聲歎息。"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可惜。", "name": "帕爾維斯"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斐爾迪南還是輸了。", "name": "帕爾維斯"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_528_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您為何會這樣想？即便我沒能攔住那幾個人，他們也終究勢單力孤。", "name": "萊茵防衛科成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_528_1#1$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我剛剛看見你的老上司回到了萊茵生命總部。", "name": "帕爾維斯"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_528_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "塞雷婭主任？！", "name": "萊茵防衛科成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_528_1#1$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘶......", "name": "萊茵防衛科成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_528_1#1$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別激動。你是不是被揍得挺狠的？誰動的手，那個警長嗎？我記得你說，她在某些地方很像塞雷婭。", "name": "帕爾維斯"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_528_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......沒有人真能和主任一樣。", "name": "萊茵防衛科成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_528_1#1$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......我只是想不明白。", "name": "萊茵防衛科成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_528_1#1$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼主任會做出那樣的選擇......我見過她工作得有多拼，她明明重視萊茵生命勝過自己的健康和名譽！", "name": "萊茵防衛科成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_528_1#1$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我一直都想像她一樣守護萊茵，可她為何棄我們而去？", "name": "萊茵防衛科成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_528_1#1$1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你怎麼知道......是她背棄了我們，而不是我們先讓她失望？", "name": "帕爾維斯"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_528_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您是說......", "name": "萊茵防衛科成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_528_1#1$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你呀，你也還年輕。", "name": "帕爾維斯"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "年輕人總是會為一時的意氣相投而聚在一起，又在之後的漫長歲月裡認清彼此。", "name": "帕爾維斯"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你別看他們現在吵得那麼厲害......在相遇的時候，他們或多或少還是真心的。", "name": "帕爾維斯"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_528_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "萊茵防衛科成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_528_1#1$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "帕爾維斯主任......您在聽音樂嗎？", "name": "萊茵防衛科成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_528_1#1$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_ltroom", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_531_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你沒聽到過這段旋律嗎？", "name": "帕爾維斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_531_1#1$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，我忘了。你來得太晚，錯過了萊茵生命的第一次新年派對。", "name": "帕爾維斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_531_1#1$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那時候......那時候的萊茵還沒有自己的大樓。", "name": "帕爾維斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_531_1#1$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "克麗斯騰租了半層辦公大樓，就在特里蒙理工大學旁邊。她和塞雷婭一起住在附近的老公寓裡。", "name": "帕爾維斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_531_1#1$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斐爾迪南總是念叨著自己要為萊茵帶來更多經費，可在他離開之前的公司之後，曾經的合作方都不常回他的郵件了。", "name": "帕爾維斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_531_1#1$1"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還沒有離開原來的研究所，每個月只有一兩次機會回到特里蒙。", "name": "帕爾維斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_531_1#1$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "新年的前一天，繆爾賽思發來消息，讓我一定要回去參加派對。", "name": "帕爾維斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_531_1#1$1"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個晚上下了很大的雪，特區回來的路上堵得很厲害，我本來不想折騰自己這把老骨頭，可繆爾賽思威脅了我。", "name": "帕爾維斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_531_1#1$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她說，要是我不按時回去，她會在新年第一天讓冰水浸透我的枕頭。", "name": "帕爾維斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_531_1#1$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在快到零點的時候，我終於踏進了那間辦公室——", "name": "帕爾維斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_531_1#1$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然後我聽到了這首歌。", "name": "帕爾維斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_531_1#1$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很難聽，真的。", "name": "帕爾維斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_531_1#1$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "作為一名萊塔尼亞人，我至今無法理解，在掌握著那般高超的源石技藝的同時，繆爾賽思對音樂的品味為何還能如此讓人不敢恭維。", "name": "帕爾維斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_531_1#1$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然而其他人好像不怎麼在乎。你敢相信嗎？斐爾迪南竟然邀請塞雷婭一起跳舞，而且塞雷婭還答應了他。", "name": "帕爾維斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_531_1#1$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "克麗斯騰......克麗斯騰只是站在一旁看著。那個晚上，她看著屋子裡的人的時間比看窗外的時間更久。", "name": "帕爾維斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_531_1#1$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那樣的日子......我都快記不清了。", "name": "帕爾維斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_531_1#1$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這歌......到底該怎麼唱來著......", "name": "帕爾維斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_531_1#1$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉......", "name": "帕爾維斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_531_1#1$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我是不是真的老了？", "name": "帕爾維斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_531_1#1$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "帕爾維斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_531_1#1$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "29_g2_edgeofbase", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_528_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "萊茵防衛科成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_528_1#1$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "主任......帕爾維斯主任？", "name": "萊茵防衛科成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_528_1#1$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您......睡著了嗎？", "name": "萊茵防衛科成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_528_1#1$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "通訊器另一頭遲遲沒有回應。"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "旋律仍在繼續，最後一個音節播完之後，又回到了最開始。"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他不知道年邁的卡普里尼是否還在通訊器旁。"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他只知道，天亮之後，等回到萊茵總部，一定能看到帕爾維斯站在老地方端著茶杯，面帶微笑，注視著樓下一張張年輕的面孔來來往往。"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}